library(readODS)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)

#  sheet 
years <- c("107", "108", "109", "110", "111")
year_labels <- c(2018, 2019, 2020, 2021, 2022)

# 
all_data <- data.frame()

# 
for (i in seq_along(years)) {
  sheet_name <- years[i]
  year <- year_labels[i]
  
  df <- read_ods("data/.ods", sheet = sheet_name, skip = 3)
  colnames(df) <- c("name", "", "", "", "", "")
  df <- df[df$name != "", ]
  df$year <- year
  all_data <- rbind(all_data, df)
}

library(readODS)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)

#  sheet 
years <- c("107", "108", "109", "110", "111")
year_labels <- c(2018, 2019, 2020, 2021, 2022)

# 
all_data <- data.frame()

# 
for (i in seq_along(years)) {
  sheet_name <- years[i]
  year <- year_labels[i]
  
  df <- read_ods("data/.ods", sheet = sheet_name, skip = 3)
  colnames(df) <- c("name", "", "", "", "", "")
  df <- df[df$name != "", ]
  df$year <- year
  all_data <- rbind(all_data, df)
}
## New names:
## New names:
## New names:
## New names:
## New names:
##  `` -> `...1`
##  `` -> `...2`
##  `` -> `...6`
# 
selected_cities <- c("Taipei City", "New Taipei City", "Taichung City", "Tainan City", "Kaohsiung City","Taoyuan")

# 
plot_data <- all_data %>% filter(name %in% selected_cities)

# 
macaron_colors <- c(
  "#FFD1DC",  # 
  "#AEE1F9",  # 
  "#C1E1C1",  # 
  "#FFF4B2",  # 
  "#E6C1E6",  # 
  "#FFDAC1"   # 
)
ggplot(plot_data, aes(x = year, y = ``, color = name)) +
  geom_line(size = 1.2) +
  geom_point(size = 2) +
  scale_color_manual(values = macaron_colors) +
  facet_wrap(~ name) +
  labs(
    title = "20182022",
    x = "", y = " (%)", color = ""
  ) +
  theme_minimal(base_family = "PingFang TC") +
  theme(
    plot.title = element_text(size = 16, face = "bold"),
    strip.text = element_text(face = "bold", size = 11),
    legend.position = "none"
  )
